c: 9
v: 71
t: "“Okhulupirira aamuna ndi okhulupirira aakazi, ndiabwenzi omvana pakati pawo. Amalamula zabwino ndikuletsa zoipa ndipo amapemphera Swala ndi kupereka chopereka (zakaat), ndipo amamvera Allah ndi Mtumiki Wake. Awo ndi omwe Allah adzawachitira chifundo. Ndithu Allah Ngwamphamvu zoposa, Ngwanzeru zakuya"